    <p style="float:none;"><strong><a href="http://weblog.mediatemple.net/2011/02/17/api-for-everyone/" target="_blank">API for Everyone!</a></strong> &mdash; We are very excited to release the ProDev API to the public. <a href="http://weblog.mediatemple.net/2011/02/17/api-for-everyone/" target="_blank">Read the ProDev API announcement!</a> <a href="#" class="closer" style="float:right">x</a></p> 
