  <div id="contentdiv" class="productpage">
    <div class="prod-subhead">
      <div class="fl-left">
        <h3 class="prod-head apibeta"><em>(mt) API. Take Control.</em></h3>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    <div id="prod-content">
      <div class="prod-lcol fl-left"> <a class="api-badge"><em>(ve) Server</em></a>
        <p class="prod-intro">The (mt) API opens up a new level of flexibility and freedom to your hosted infrastructure. Access statistics, reboot servers, check billing status, all via an interface that gives <i>you</i> the controls to make it your own. <a href="https://ac.mediatemple.net/api" class="highlighter">Get Started with the (mt) API &raquo;</a></p>
        <div class="prod-highlights">
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p><strong>Features you Want</strong> 
              You wanted an API. Here&rsquo;s the <a href="http://wiki.mediatemple.net/w/Category:API" title="(mt) API Documentation">first look</a> at the interface that will give you even more control over your (mt) hosting services.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><strong>Feedback Driven</strong> 
              We built the API to make your life managing servers easier, so <a href="https://forums.mediatemple.net">your feedback</a> helps us decide what to add next.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><strong>Ask and Receive</strong> 
              Create your level of control your way, the (mt) API returns JSON or XML via top-speed Jersey/Grails-powered RESTful interface.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p><strong>More to come!</strong> 
              Compatibility with other popular cloud APIs, controls for all (mt) products, provisioning controls and more are on the horizon.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="clearfix">&nbsp;</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prod-rcol fl-right">
        <div class="prod-features">
          <h4>API Features:</h4>
          <ul class="largelist apibeta">
            <li class="status">Realtime server status</li>
            <li class="reboot">Reboot VPS servers</li>
            <li class="disk">List hostnames &amp; services</li>
            <li class="secure">Securely reset passwords</li>
            <li class="interface">RESTful interface</li>
            <li class="lastli more">And more!</li>
          </ul>
          
          <ul class="prod-sidelinks" style="padding-top:20px;">
            <li>
              <a href="http://wiki.mediatemple.net/w/Category:API" class="sidelink-apidocs" style="margin-bottom: 10px"><em>View API Documentation</em></a>
            </li>
          </ul>
          
        </div>
